title: Aspire Gaming Diamond/Plat Team searching for support
body:
Hello,
Our team Aspire Gaming "AG" is searching a support. 
We created the team dec 2015 and we played some tournament already and want to keep that up.

What conditions do you need?
-plat/diamond player
-good champion pool
-able to take criticism
-fun in playing the game

the team consists of plat players:
Top: in game names: Sad Toplaner          Plat 4
Jungle:                         OC Onkelmon         Plat 4
Mid:                             AG iyanu ìtàgé         Plat 3
ADC:                            Tisuke                      Plat 1

add "Tisuke" for tryouts 
EDIT: wir sind ein deutsches team, also keine angst der post ist englisch um mehr zu erreichen
